# UL_JUNCTION

## Data members

| | |
| --- | --- |
| diameter | int |
| x, y | int (center point) |

See also UL_SEGMENT

## Example

```
schematic(SCH) {
 SCH.sheets(SH) {
 SH.nets(N) {
 N.segments(SEG) {
 SEG.junctions(J) {
 printf("Junction: (%f %f)\n", u2mm(J.x), u2mm(J.y));
 }
 }
 }
 }
 }
```





